## 2.1.0 (2023-09-08)

### 注意：Windows 用户请以管理员权限运行 pot 之后再更新

### Note: For Windows users, please run pot with administrator privileges before updating.

### New feature:

-   Add Clipboard Monitor([`a6a41cd`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/a6a41cd9f272785a68f36df236286fad7ce506db)) (by @Pylogmon)
-   Support Local Backup([`72806cb`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/72806cb01545ba5c6b43f469b6723c2099f370b2)) (by @Pylogmon)
-   Choose Translate Window Position([`86869f8`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/86869f884cc47eba1f44208384707a1aeaf009c0)) (by @Pylogmon)
-   Switch Transparent Effect([`15e7a26`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/15e7a2669a7d573ac70fd2d3f1524e50432537f4)) (by @Pylogmon)

### Bugs fixed:

-   Crash when Add Service([`b952e61`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/b952e61e9281a15d603daa2ed0cefdfdf22f7997)) (by @Pylogmon)
-   Copy Text Failed when Recognize([`738b535`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/738b535ffacea32cad9a954cbf84c4f0b9c4f69f)) (by @Pylogmon)
-   Can't Input on some Platform([`79b09e1`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/79b09e13139678c46293f2f2c729c4713dae32a6)) (by @Pylogmon)
-   Init Language Model when Use Baidu([`5eed62b`](https://github.com/pot-app/pot-desktop/commit/5eed62bc2af26f889dafde809dd6cbc288cc0138)) (by @Pylogmon)
